                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p><add>?</add> ser</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia, Pa</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p><add>?</add> Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The motive I have<lb/> in addressing you is the<lb/> following I\n                have heard so<lb/> much about the history of<lb/> our creed but could never<lb/> get\n                a <sic>definit</sic> history of the<lb/> same further than the<lb/> old Testament I\n                am firm<lb/> believer of the old Testament<lb/> but would like to\n                <sic>reade</sic><lb/> some english books which<lb/> would give me some light<lb/> of\n                our history since the<lb/> same was written I have<lb/> heard <sic>agread</sic> many\n                things<lb/> about <persName>Jesus Christ</persName> from<lb/> different sources can\n                you<lb/> inform me how I could</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3571847t/canvas/p1"
